title: TVS Motor rolls out 2023 TVS Apache RTR 160 4V priced at Rs 1.30 lakh
description: TVS Motor Company rolled out a 2023 Special Edition of its popular motorcycle 160 4V Apache RTR on Tuesday. It is equipped with a host of features, said the firm. The 2023 TVS Apache RTR 160 4V Special Edition comes in a pearl white colour and is priced at Rs 1.30 lakh (ex-showroom Delhi) and available at its dealerships across the country.
